INSERT INTO `blog_translations` VALUES (30,28,'en','How to Register on the NJI Learning Platform','<p>In this article, Ill guide you through the simple steps to register on the NJI Learning Platform. By following these two straightforward rules, youll gain access to a wealth of resources tailored to enhance your judicial knowledge and professional growth.</p>','<p>Creating an account on the NJI Learning Platform is simple and ensures you gain access to a wealth of resources tailored for legal and judicial professionals. Follow these steps to get started:</p><h3><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\"><br></span></h3><h3><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Step 1: Click on Register</span></h3><p>Begin by visiting the NJI Learning Platform homepage and clicking the \"Register\" button. This will take you to the sign-up page where you can create your account.</p><p><br></p><p><img src=\"https://nji.sapphitalgroup.net/store/1075/Screenshot%202025-01-24%20091511.png\" style=\"width: 1022.22px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder; font-size: 1.75rem;\"><br></span></p><p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder; font-size: 1.75rem;\">Step 2: Enter Your Details</span></p><p>On the registration page, provide the following details:</p><ul><li><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Full Name:</span>&nbsp;Enter your official name as it appears in your professional records.</li><li><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Email Address:</span>&nbsp;Use a valid email address you can access regularly.</li><li><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Password:</span>&nbsp;Choose a strong password that is secure and easy for you to remember.</li></ul><p>Once all fields are completed, click on the&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">\"Sign Up\"</span>&nbsp;button to proceed.<br><br><br><img src=\"https://nji.sapphitalgroup.net/store/1075/Screenshot%202025-01-23%20143614.png\" style=\"width: 1022.22px;\"><br></p><h3><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\"><br></span></h3><h3><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Step 3: Verify Your Email</span></h3><p>After signing up, a verification email will be sent to the address you provided. Open the email and follow the instructions to verify your account. This may include entering a verification code.<br><br><img src=\"https://nji.sapphitalgroup.net/store/1075/Screenshot%202025-01-23%20143949.png\" style=\"width: 1022.22px;\"><br></p><h3><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Step 4: Access Your Dashboard</span></h3><p>Once your email is verified, youll have full access to your personalized dashboard. Here, you can explore courses, track your progress, and connect with other professionals on the platform.</p><p>By completing these steps, youll be fully registered and ready to begin your learning journey with the NJI Learning Platform. If you encounter any issues during registration, feel free to contact support for assistance.</p><p><img src=\"https://nji.sapphitalgroup.net/store/1075/Screenshot%202025-01-23%20144102.png\" style=\"width: 1022.22px;\"><br></p><p>Ready to get started? Click&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Register</span>&nbsp;today!</p>','In this article, Ill guide you through the simple steps to register on the NJI Learning Platform. By following these two straightforward rules, youll gain access to a wealth of resources tailored to enhance your judicial knowledge and professional growth.'),(31,29,'en','Enroll in any course with these easy steps','<p>In this article, Ill explain the steps to enroll in a course on the NJI Learning Platform. If you follow my advice, youll unlock valuable learning opportunities while staying organized and efficient in your professional development.</p>','<h3><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Step 1: Log In to Your Account</span></h3><p>Begin by logging into your account on the NJI Learning Platform using your email and password. If you dont have an account yet, refer to the guide on creating an account.</p><hr><h3><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Step 2: Browse Available Courses</span></h3><p>Once logged in, click on the&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Courses</span>&nbsp;tab in the navigation menu. Youll see a catalog of courses categorized by topic or area of interest. Use the search bar or filters to find the course that suits your needs.</p><p><img src=\"https://nji.sapphitalgroup.net/store/1075/Screenshot%202025-01-24%20090641.png\" style=\"width: 1022.22px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder; font-size: 1.75rem;\"><br></span></p><p><img src=\"https://nji.sapphitalgroup.net/store/1075/Screenshot%202025-01-24%20091036.png\" style=\"width: 1022.22px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder; font-size: 1.75rem;\"><br></span></p><p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder; font-size: 1.75rem;\">Step 3: Review Course Details</span></p><p>Click on the course youre interested in to view its description. Read through the objectives, curriculum, and requirements to ensure it aligns with your goals.</p><h3><img src=\"https://nji.sapphitalgroup.net/store/1075/Screenshot%202025-01-23%20155622.png\" style=\"width: 1022.22px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder; font-size: 1.75rem;\"><br></span></h3><h3><span style=\"font-weight: bolder; font-size: 1.75rem;\">Step 4: Enroll in the Course</span></h3><ul><li>If the course is&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">free</span>, simply click on the&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Enroll</span>&nbsp;button, and youll be automatically enrolled.</li><li>If the course is&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">paid</span>, you will be redirected to a secure payment page. Complete the payment process to confirm your enrollment.</li><li>You can then click on the \" Go to Learning Page\" button to begin learning immediately&nbsp;</li></ul><h3><img src=\"https://nji.sapphitalgroup.net/store/1075/Screenshot%202025-01-23%20155654.png\" style=\"width: 1022.22px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\"><br></span></h3><h3><img src=\"https://nji.sapphitalgroup.net/store/1075/Screenshot%202025-01-24%20091212.png\" style=\"width: 1022.22px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\"><br></span></h3><h3><span style=\"font-weight: bolder; font-size: 1.75rem;\">Step 5: Access All Your Enrolled Courses</span></h3><p>If you want to access all your enrolled courses,&nbsp; navigate to your dashboard and click on the&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Purchased Courses</span>&nbsp;section on your personalized dashboard. Here, youll find all the courses youre enrolled in. Select any course to begin learning at your convenience.</p><p><img src=\"https://nji.sapphitalgroup.net/store/1075/Screenshot%202025-01-24%20091800.png\" style=\"width: 1022.22px;\"><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><img src=\"https://nji.sapphitalgroup.net/store/1075/Screenshot%202025-01-24%20091854.png\" style=\"width: 1022.22px;\"><br></p><p>By following these steps, you can easily start accessing the knowledge and resources you need to enhance your legal expertise. If you encounter any issues during enrollment, dont hesitate to contact the support team for assistance.</p><p></p><p>Start exploring your courses today and take the next step in your professional development!</p>','In this article, Ill explain the steps to enroll in a course on the NJI Learning Platform. If you follow my advice, youll unlock valuable learning opportunities while staying organized and efficient in your professional development.'),(32,30,'en','How to access your certificates on the platform','<p>In this article, Ill guide you through the simple steps to access your certificate on the NJI</p>','<p>After successfully completing a course on the NJI Learning Platform, you can easily access your certificate of completion. Follow these steps to view and manage your certificates:</p><hr><h3><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Step 1: Complete the Course</span></h3><p>Ensure that you have completed the course with 100% progress. Certificates are only generated once all course requirements are fulfilled.</p><h3><img src=\"https://nji.sapphitalgroup.net/store/1075/Screenshot%202025-01-24%20094521.png\" style=\"width: 1022.22px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder; font-size: 1.75rem;\">Step 2: Access the Certificate Button</span></h3><p>On the course learning page, locate the&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Certificate</span>&nbsp;button. Click on it and then select&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Show</span>&nbsp;to view your certificate.</p><h3><img src=\"https://nji.sapphitalgroup.net/store/1075/Screenshot%202025-01-24%20094553.png\" style=\"width: 1022.22px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder; font-size: 1.75rem;\">Step 3: View All Certificates</span></h3><p>To see all your earned certificates:</p><ol><li>Navigate to your&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Dashboard</span>.</li><li>Click on the&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Certificates</span>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Certificates of Completion</span>&nbsp;section.</li></ol><p><img src=\"https://nji.sapphitalgroup.net/store/1075/humm.png\" style=\"width: 1022.22px;\"><br></p><p>Here, youll find a list of all certificates tied to your completed courses.</p><hr><h3><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Step 4: Open Certificates</span></h3><p>Select any certificate from the list and click&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Open</span>&nbsp;to view it in detail. Each certificate comes with a unique ID for verification and authentication purposes.</p><hr><p>By following these steps, you can showcase your achievements and download certificates for your records. If you face any challenges while accessing certificates, the support team is always ready to assist.</p><p><img src=\"https://nji.sapphitalgroup.net/store/1075/Screenshot%202025-01-24%20095013.png\" style=\"width: 1022.22px;\"><br><br>Start earning your certificates today by completing your courses!</p>','In this article, Ill guide you through the simple steps to access your certificate on the NJI');
