INSERT INTO `page_translations` VALUES (1,3,'en','About NJI LMS','Discover the National Judicial Institute Academy, Nigerias premier platform for judicial education and professional development. Learn about our mission to advance judicial excellence through innovative programs.','<h4><strong>About the National Judicial Institute Academy</strong></h4><p>The <strong>National Judicial Institute Academy (NJIA)</strong> is dedicated to advancing judicial excellence through education, research, and capacity-building initiatives. We serve as the premier platform for judicial officers, legal practitioners, and justice sector stakeholders to acquire the knowledge and skills necessary to uphold the rule of law and ensure the delivery of fair and efficient justice.</p><h4><strong>Our Vision</strong></h4><p>To be the leading institution for judicial education and professional development in Nigeria and beyond.</p><h4><strong>Our Mission</strong></h4><p>To enhance the performance of the judiciary through innovative learning programs, specialized training, and access to cutting-edge resources.</p><h4><strong>What We Offer</strong></h4><ul><li><strong>Judicial Training Programs</strong>: Courses tailored to the unique needs of judicial officers and court personnel.</li><li><strong>Workshops and Seminars</strong>: Interactive sessions led by renowned legal experts.</li><li><strong>Research Resources</strong>: Access to critical legal studies and insights.</li><li><strong>Professional Development Opportunities</strong>: Certifications, networking, and skill-building events.</li></ul><p>Join us at NJIA to elevate your judicial expertise and contribute to the advancement of justice in Nigeria and beyond.</p>'),(2,5,'en','Terms of Service','Read the terms and conditions governing your use of the National Judicial Institute Academy platform. Learn about account responsibilities, reward policies, and data protection guidelines.','<h4><strong>Welcome to the National Judicial Institute Academy</strong></h4><p>These terms and conditions govern your access to and use of the <strong>National Judicial Institute Academy (NJIA)</strong> platform, including our website, mobile applications, and related services (Services).</p><h4><strong>Account Requirements</strong></h4><ul><li>To access NJIA courses and resources, you must create an account with accurate and complete information, including a valid email address.</li><li>You are responsible for maintaining the confidentiality of your account credentials and for all activities associated with your account.</li><li>NJIA reserves the right to suspend or terminate accounts for misuse or violation of these terms.</li></ul><h4><strong>Reward Points System</strong></h4><ul><li>Points earned through the Reward System are non-transferable and must be redeemed in accordance with our reward policies.</li><li>NJIA reserves the right to modify or discontinue the Reward Points System at its discretion.</li></ul><h4><strong>Content Usage</strong></h4><ul><li>All content on the NJIA platform is for personal and professional development purposes only.</li><li>You may not reproduce, share, or distribute NJIA content without prior written permission.</li></ul><h4><strong>Privacy and Data Protection</strong></h4><p>NJIA is committed to safeguarding your personal information. Please refer to our <strong>Privacy Policy</strong> for details on data collection, use, and protection.</p><h4><strong>Disclaimer</strong></h4><p>NJIA strives to provide accurate and up-to-date content; however, we make no guarantees regarding the completeness or reliability of the material.</p><p>By using our platform, you agree to comply with these terms. Violations may result in account suspension or other actions deemed necessary by NJIA.</p>'),(3,6,'en','Reward Points System','Earn points as you learn with the National Judicial Institute Academy. Enroll in courses, engage in activities, and redeem rewards for exclusive resources, events, and certifications.','<h4><strong>Empowering Learning Through Rewards</strong></h4><p>The <strong>National Judicial Institute Academy (NJIA)</strong> Reward System is designed to recognize and encourage the dedication of our learners. By actively engaging with the academys resources and completing educational milestones, participants can earn points that unlock exclusive benefits.</p><h4><strong>How It Works</strong></h4><ul><li><strong>Enroll in a Course</strong>: Earn points for every course registration.</li><li><strong>Complete a Course</strong>: Finish a course and earn additional rewards for your commitment.</li><li><strong>Provide Feedback</strong>: Share course reviews and evaluations to gain more points.</li><li><strong>Refer a Colleague</strong>: Invite fellow legal professionals to join and earn points when they enroll.</li></ul><h4><strong>Redeeming Your Points</strong></h4><p>Reward points can be redeemed for:</p><ul><li>Discounts on specialized courses or workshops.</li><li>Access to exclusive judicial resources and publications.</li><li>Invitations to premium events, webinars, or seminars.</li><li>Certification benefits such as waived fees for advanced programs.</li></ul><h4><strong>Why Use the Reward System?</strong></h4><p>The reward system fosters continuous professional growth, strengthens engagement, and provides a tangible acknowledgment of learners\' efforts in enhancing their legal expertise.</p><p>Start earning points today and enjoy the benefits of your learning journey with NJIA!</p><h3></h3><hr>'),(4,5,'es','Trminos de servicio','Nuestra misin es mejorar vidas a travs del aprendizaje. Permitimos que cualquier persona en cualquier lugar pueda crear y compartir contenido educativo (instructores) y acceder a ese contenido educativo para aprender.','<p>Nota: Estos son solo datos de demostracin.</p><p><br></p><p>Nuestra misin es mejorar vidas a travs del aprendizaje. Permitimos que cualquier persona en cualquier lugar pueda crear y compartir contenido educativo (instructores) y acceder a ese contenido educativo para aprender (estudiantes). Consideramos nuestro modelo de mercado la mejor manera de ofrecer contenido educativo valioso a nuestros usuarios. Necesitamos reglas para mantener nuestra plataforma y servicios seguros para usted, nosotros y nuestra comunidad de estudiantes e instructores. Estos Trminos se aplican a todas sus actividades en el sitio web de Udemy, las aplicaciones mviles de Udemy, nuestras aplicaciones de TV, nuestras API y otros servicios relacionados (\"Servicios\").</p><p><br></p><p>Si publica contenido en nuestra plataforma, tambin debe aceptar los Trminos del instructor. Tambin proporcionamos detalles sobre nuestro procesamiento de los datos personales de nuestros estudiantes e instructores en nuestra Poltica de privacidad. Si utiliza nuestra plataforma para empresas como parte de la suscripcin a Udemy for Business de su organizacin, debe consultar nuestra Declaracin de privacidad de Udemy for Business.</p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p>Necesita una cuenta para la mayora de las actividades en nuestra plataforma, incluso para comprar y acceder a contenido o para enviar contenido para su publicacin. Al configurar y mantener su cuenta, debe proporcionar y continuar proporcionando informacin precisa y completa, incluida una direccin de correo electrnico vlida. Usted es completamente responsable de su cuenta y de todo lo que sucede en ella, incluido cualquier dao o perjuicio (a nosotros o a cualquier otra persona) causado por alguien que usa su cuenta sin su permiso. Esto significa que debe tener cuidado con su contrasea. No puede transferir su cuenta a otra persona ni usar la cuenta de otra persona. Si se comunica con nosotros para solicitar acceso a una cuenta, no le otorgaremos dicho acceso a menos que pueda proporcionarnos la informacin que necesitamos para demostrar que es el propietario de esa cuenta. En caso de fallecimiento de un usuario, la cuenta de ese usuario se cerrar.</p>'),(5,